 signal. For a\nbenchmark scenario with $W^{ \\pm }_R$ of mass 2 TeV and singlet neutrino of\nmass 750 GeV, we find that, in both the di-lepton + di-jet + Higgs and\ntri-lepton + Higgs channels, significant evidence can be seen at the LHC14 for\nan integrated luminosity of 300/fb and that even discovery is possible with\nslightly more luminosity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Dec 2016 20:59:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-02"}
