frared filters show how one can separate\nevolved stars from young stellar objects (YSOs) and distinguish among different\nYSO classes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Dec 2016 21:36:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-13"}
