and of\nsimilar objects) are described by the same \"disk plus Comptonized blackbody\"\nmodel, but with considerably different parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2016 04:37:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-21"}
