hout heavy elements and reveals that the\ncharge-transfer efficiency across the intramolecular interface strongly depends\non the surplus excitation energy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2016 12:52:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-16"}
