 the potential key role of corotation\nresonances in the dynamical evolution of close-in star-planet or binary\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2016 14:08:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-16"}
